&lt;p&gt;I am using R and tried &lt;code&gt;some.function&lt;/code&gt; but I got following error message:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-r s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-r&quot;&gt;Error&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; could not find &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot;&gt;&quot;some.function&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This question comes up very regularly. When you get this type of error in R, how can you solve it?&lt;/p&gt;
